Package: refreshtdaccesstoken
Title: Get Access Token from TD Ameritrade via Stored Refresh Token
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person( "Munair", "Simpson", email = "munair@gmail.com", role = c( "aut", "cre" ) )
Description: This function uses an API key and a monthly generated Refresh Token saved to an RDS file to generate an Access Token using a TD Ameritrade REST API endpoint. The Access Token generated is good for 30 minutes. An HTTP request's authorization header uses this access token [preceded by "Bearer "] to retrieve data from TD Ameritrade's REST API servers.
License: `use_gpl3_license()`
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list( markdown = TRUE )
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: httr
